    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Global Digital Niaga Tbk operates an omnichannel commerce and lifestyle platform in Indonesia. The company operates through First Party, Third Party, Institution, and Physical Store segments. It trades in merchandise through electronic media network under the Blibli.com brand. The company also offers logistics; trading; online financial transaction; information and communication and travel agency; transportation and warehousing; portal web and digital platform; reservation; movie playing; software publishing; cold storage; management and handling; application development and computer and management consulting; photography; and advertising services. In addition, it engages in the wholesale trading of software, telecommunication equipment, and computer equipment; retail of telecommunication equipment and media-based products, and computer and equipment; supermarket operation; real estate leasing; software development; accommodation and tour; and business management, marketing, and sales support businesses. Further, the company trades in furniture and housing products; sale of land; and furniture manufacturing, construction, and installation business. PT Global Digital Niaga Tbk was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Kudus, Indonesia. PT Global Digital Niaga Tbk is a subsidiary of Pt Global Investama Andalan.",
